name: Soliloquy
description:
This illustration express a manifestation of the unconscious desire, through a replica of one's own unknown face since as one side of the personality is repressed.

Esta ilustración expresa una manifestación del deseo inconsciente, a través de una réplica del propio rostro desconocido ya que un lado de la personalidad es reprimida.

The UNTITLED series by Claudia Vasquez/Doppelwuanger, 2021.
